This will hinder our progress.

38
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:53,800
My child!

39
00:01:56,600 --> 00:01:57,520
Weiwei.

40
00:01:58,440 --> 00:01:59,880
You are also a victim.

41
00:02:01,560 --> 00:02:03,480
Your parents abandoned you
when you were little.

42
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:06,400
Your grandma who raised you passed away.

43
00:02:07,360 --> 00:02:08,640
