to exchange for drug money.

58
00:02:45,920 --> 00:02:46,840
Sister.

59
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:48,400
Come with us.

60
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:49,920
Let's go home together.

61
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:55,160
Go home?

62
00:02:58,320 --> 00:02:59,440
