come to my house.

64
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:04,960
My house is big.

65
00:03:04,960 --> 00:03:07,440
My parents will take care of you.

66
00:03:07,440 --> 00:03:10,160
They can also be your parents.

67
00:03:14,200 --> 00:03:15,640
The people inside!

68
00:03:16,640 --> 00:03:18,600
Please, let my daughter go!

69
00:03:20,400 --> 00:03:22,040
