72
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:28,760
I beg you.

73
00:03:28,760 --> 00:03:30,440
Please let my daughter go.

74
00:03:30,760 --> 00:03:33,680
- I'll give you whatever you want.
- Xiaolei, An'an.

75
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:34,880
Please let her go.

76
00:03:34,880 --> 00:03:35,920
I beg you.

77
00:03:35,920 --> 00:03:36,960
Leave now.

78
00:03:36,960 --> 00:03:39,020
I beg you.

79
00:03:46,040 --> 00:03:46,960
Weiwei.

80
00:03:47,920 --> 00:03:49,040
