84
00:03:58,680 --> 00:03:59,600
Who am I?

85
00:04:01,600 --> 00:04:03,560
I am everything I can perceive.

86
00:04:05,600 --> 00:04:06,640
Who am I?

87
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,640
