90
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:20,960
If I could be reborn,

91
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:24,280
I would hope

92
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:27,880
to become a light, shimmering firefly,

93
00:04:28,400 --> 00:04:30,040
