94
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:34,280
- Even if it's faint,
- Even if it's faint,

95
00:04:35,810 --> 00:04:37,580
- it would still warm.
- it would still warm.

96
00:04:41,080 --> 00:04:42,440
This is the poem you wrote

97
00:04:42,440 --> 00:04:43,680
for the competition, remember?

98
00:04:46,240 --> 00:04:48,360
Even though life has been unfair to you,

99
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:49,200
you still hope

100
00:04:49,200 --> 00:04:50,960
to bring warmth to those around you.

101
00:04:53,520 --> 00:04:54,680
You did it.

102
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:57,040
No matter what happened just now,

103
00:04:58,200 --> 00:04:59,320
before this,

104
00:04:59,760 --> 00:05:01,800
you were always taking care of Xiaolei

105
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:02,840
and An'an.

106
00:05:03,880 --> 00:05:04,800
Right?

107
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:09,560
I also heard about a poem.

108
00:05:09,960 --> 00:05:11,680
You must have heard of it too.

109
00:05:12,280 --> 00:05:13,480
With one bit of heat,

110
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:15,640
give off one bit of light.

111
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:19,080
Like a firefly,

112
00:05:20,960 --> 00:05:22,160
giving off a bit of light

113
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:24,920
in the darkness.

114
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:29,440
No need to wait for a torch.

115
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:31,800
From now on,

116
00:05:33,120 --> 00:05:34,760
if there is no torch,

117
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:39,080
I will be the only light.

118
