229
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:26,680
You're full of it.

230
00:12:26,680 --> 00:12:28,520
You always say that after every training.

231
00:12:29,480 --> 00:12:30,440
What about you?

232
00:12:30,680 --> 00:12:33,560
You always say you're swift and agile,

233
00:12:34,680 --> 00:12:36,240
like a living swallow

234
00:12:36,240 --> 00:12:37,760
and the modern female Ye Wen.

235
00:12:42,760 --> 00:12:43,680
Am I like Ye Wen?

236
00:12:44,090 --> 00:12:45,660
- Do I look like Ye Wen?
- Stop joking.

237
00:12:46,120 --> 00:12:47,040
Captain.

238
00:12:47,180 --> 00:12:48,040
Captain.

239
00:12:48,040 --> 00:12:49,640
Sit down. Let's have some water.

240
00:12:49,940 --> 00:12:51,120
- Thanks, Captain.
- Take it.

241
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:52,040
Thanks, Captain.

242
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:55,360
I've got some good news for all of you.

243
00:12:55,760 --> 00:12:56,600
Yu Weiwei's mom

244
00:12:56,600 --> 00:12:58,040
has settled everything at home.

245
00:12:58,040 --> 00:12:59,410
She's ready to bring her back home.

246
00:12:59,720 --> 00:13:01,080
Also, both sides of the parents

247
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:02,760
have guaranteed the team leaders

248
00:13:03,120 --> 00:13:05,080
that they will make sure
Weiwei goes to college.

249
00:13:05,320 --> 00:13:06,520
They'll share the difficulties

250
00:13:06,520 --> 00:13:08,200
and help her through this sensitive period.

251
00:13:08,520 --> 00:13:09,400
At times like these,

252
00:13:09,400 --> 00:13:10,910
I feel so proud to be a police officer.

253
00:13:10,920 --> 00:13:13,320
It feels really great
to be able to help others.

254
00:13:13,320 --> 00:13:14,240
Yes.

255
00:13:14,480 --> 00:13:16,080
My parents are both police officers.

256
00:13:16,080 --> 00:13:17,720
When I was little, I never understood

257
00:13:17,720 --> 00:13:19,840
why they never had time to spend with me.

258
00:13:20,480 --> 00:13:22,280
Now that I'm a police officer too,

259
00:13:22,960 --> 00:13:24,600
I finally understand them.

260
00:13:28,040 --> 00:13:28,960
Tata.

261
00:13:30,280 --> 00:13:31,640
Why are you silent again?

262
00:13:35,520 --> 00:13:35,990
It's good.

263
00:13:37,280 --> 00:13:38,240
Tata.

264
00:13:38,240 --> 00:13:39,710
- Where are you going?
- What are you doing?

265
00:13:39,710 --> 00:13:40,560
What?

266
00:13:40,560 --> 00:13:41,480
Extra training.

267
00:13:42,480 --> 00:13:43,400
Extra training?

268
00:13:43,400 --> 00:13:44,880
You're just gonna watch?

269
00:13:45,680 --> 00:13:46,640
Captain.

270
00:13:46,640 --> 00:13:47,560
Captain, we...

271
00:13:47,760 --> 00:13:48,680
My leg...

272
