273
00:13:53,200 --> 00:13:55,040
We're equipped with various firearms

274
00:13:55,040 --> 00:13:56,880
and have trained in their use.

275
00:13:57,400 --> 00:13:59,320
But I hope you'll learn more

276
00:13:59,320 --> 00:14:01,000
how to avoid using them.

277
00:14:01,460 --> 00:14:02,480
Everyone should understand

278
00:14:02,760 --> 00:14:03,680
our goal

279
00:14:03,960 --> 00:14:05,240
is never to shoot,

280
00:14:05,240 --> 00:14:06,360
but to save lives.

281
00:14:06,680 --> 00:14:07,680
Even if we shoot,

282
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:09,280
it's to stop killing.

283
00:14:10,320 --> 00:14:12,000
If we didn't have weapons today,

284
00:14:12,320 --> 00:14:13,500
could we complete the mission?

285
00:14:13,800 --> 00:14:15,200
The answer is yes.

286
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:17,680
We need to train our judgment

287
00:14:18,000 --> 00:14:20,480
by observing the words
and actions of the target

288
00:14:20,480 --> 00:14:22,320
to understand their demands,

